agent.description: Green Lane Property Ltd is the culmination of over 25 years' experience in the Estate Agency Sector. Our experience includes extensive dealings with; Residential and Commercial Sales, Residential and Commercial Lettings, Property Sourcing, Property Management, Marketing and Advertising. As property specialists, we have a wide portfolio of clients that include Individuals, Businesses and Housing Associations, with experience working alongside Contractors, Legal Services, and other Agents. Affording not only a wealth of practical experience but also providing an extensive range of contacts and sources throughout the Property Sales and Letting field.
